{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9e26e20965","title":"上海东方红电影制片厂领导小组关于殷子问题的审查报告","origin":"根据档案材料翻印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"30b33033ec","index":0,"year":1970,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"9e26e20965"}],"tags":[{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"eb87a9588f","name":"四川文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9fa2731d28","type":"title","text":"上海东方红电影制片厂领导小组关于殷子问题的审查报告","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"18d3a97fc8","type":"paragraph","text":"殷子，曾用名：项爱如、项文案，女，51岁，浙江瑞安，家庭出身：自由职业，本人成份：职员，原任天马电影制片厂付导演，文艺九级。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"ceb0f61d8a","type":"subtitle","text":"简历：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"b7699eb848","type":"paragraph","text":"1936年6月—9月，伪国民政府教育部，监时顾用书记。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"a710e37f5b","type":"paragraph","text":"1936年11月—1938年初，伪四川省教育厅书记或办事员。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"4873deaf1a","type":"paragraph","text":"1938年4月—5月，伪四川省政府旅行剧团演员。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"922c92117e","type":"paragraph","text":"1939年参加伪四川省政府和四川三青团支部举办的四川战地乡村服务团。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"7d9dd0d4ae","type":"paragraph","text":"1940年参加由国民党伪成都航空委员会政治部控制的神鹰剧团任演员。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"652eb00a9c","type":"paragraph","text":"1941年人仍属伪航委政治部空军军士学校长虹剧社任演员。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"43233adb63","type":"paragraph","text":"1943年初，参加伪成都行辕政治部前锋剧团任演员，并同时在伪军官学校血花剧社任特约演员。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"0452dcdf6b","type":"paragraph","text":"1944年3月，进伪中宣部“中电剧团”任演员。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"cd72877d9f","type":"paragraph","text":"1945年春到北京参加伪中电三厂任演员。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"b9833dd7f5","type":"paragraph","text":"1948年1月参加国民党联勤总司令特种勤务署军中演剧一队任上尉队员（以后改为国防部新闻局军中演剧队）","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"31e6551b8f","type":"paragraph","text":"1949年5月—10月，南京市工作委员会文工团演员。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"59f521bf38","type":"paragraph","text":"1949年11月至今，上海电影制片厂、天马电影厂演员。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"26ddbc4d19","type":"subtitle","text":"家庭主要成员及社会关系：","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"89e7315234","type":"paragraph","text":"殷若兰：母，家务。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"33617eb6e7","type":"paragraph","text":"齐衡：爱人，原天马电影厂演员。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"944897e644","type":"paragraph","text":"项日烨：女，青海德合哈■西州。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"719337ea42","type":"paragraph","text":"项日槐：子，吉林四平专区梨树县。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"de832a9a26","type":"paragraph","text":"项文兰：妹妹，申新五厂子弟小学教员。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"46cf221e9d","type":"subtitle","text":"主要问题及处理意见：","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"e11dc5bdb1","type":"paragraph","text":"殷子长期在国民党军队办的剧团（社）内任演员。1948年1月参加国民党联勤总司令特种勤务署军中演剧一队任上尉演员。经多方核实，未发现有其他政治活动和罪行，与本人交代基本相符。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"d23b0954c4","type":"paragraph","text":"经革命群众和领导小组研究，认为殷子的问题构不成政历问题，不予作结论。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"},{"id":"4a3173e1f3","type":"paragraph","text":" 上海东方红电影制片厂领导小组工宣队：桂恒业军宣队：任和义厂革会：管耕1970年9月","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965"}],"page":{"id":"cc8f4ea89c","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e26e20965","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}